@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_dwngsq(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (v2 * ((v0 + 0.22 - v0 + 0.29) * v1))
    v0 = (wp.exp(wp.cos(v1 + 0.85)) - (0.15 + (v0 + 0.55 / v2 + 0.20)))
    v0 = tmp
    v0 = (((v1 + 0.81 + v2 + 0.14) / (v0 + 0.95 * v2 + 0.50)) + v0)
    data[tid] = v0
